meta {
  name: Publish a security event token
  type: http
  seq: 1
}

post {
  url: {{orgUrl}}/security/api/v1/security-events
  body: none
  auth: none
}

headers {
  Accept: application/json
}

docs {
Publishes a security event token (SET) sent by a security events provider. After the token is verified, Okta ingests the event and performs any appropriate action.

**Responses:**
- `202`: Accepted
- `400`: Bad Request
}
